                    "line_text": "Achève sa péroraison.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 47,
                    "line_text": "Brigadier, lui répond l'Histoire,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 48,
                    "line_text": "Brigadier, vous avez raison !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "D'une manière péremptoire\nAchève sa péroraison.\nBrigadier, lui répond l'Histoire,\nBrigadier, vous avez raison !"
